N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 11.170 - Definition

State Regulations

The term public health social worker shall mean a social worker who identifies, assesses and manages social problems relating to illness and disability, the receipt of medical care and the attainment and maintenance of health. Notes
